import React from 'react'
import ContactImg from "../images/contact.jpeg"
import Hero from '../Components/Hero'
import Footer from '../Components/OuterComponents/Footer.js'
import ContactForm from '../Components/OuterComponents/ContactForm'

export default function Contact() {
  return (
    <>
      <Hero 
        cName="hero-mid"
        shadow = "shadow-mid"
        heroImg = {ContactImg}
        title="Contact Us"
        text="We provide the best education to our students."
        btnClass="btn"
        buttonText = "Get Enrolled"
        url="/"
      />
      <ContactForm/>
      <Footer/>
    </>
  )
}
